extendedInfo.description: This is a simple but exciting fast pace running game. You got three characters to choose. Different level brings different fast experience to you:Fat Boy - Stubborn but FunnyStick Man - Agile and good at rollingNinja - super fast like flyingGame Mechanic:1.Touch left to make the character to roll once 2.Touch right to jump. During jumping, the longer you keep touching, the farther you will jump.Goal:1.Try your best to avoid the obstacles2.Rank the first among global players 3.Get all the achievementsFinally:you will find your reaction become huge improvedWelcome follow my facebook page, there are many fun and free games to be released:http://www.facebook.com/pages/EasyFunGame/136613793102793

reviews.title: Love it or hate it.
reviews.comment: This is one of those games you either love or really hate.  Alot like another more polished one with consistant maps.  The randomness of the runs and the dying to impossible jumps make this game aggravating. Only one worth playing is the ninja.  The fat guy has no benefit and the middle one is only slightly better. The ninja is clearly the best so there is no reason to choose. This game would be so much better if the maps were consistent and you had tactical advantages for the fat and middle guy.
